1. *Skupo* je kupiti ovaj telefon. (It is expensive to buy this phone.)
2. Kupovina ovog auta me je koštala *skupo*. (Buying this car cost me dearly.)
3. Cena ovog nakita je zaista *skupa*. (The price of this jewelry is really high.)
4. *Skupom* cijenom prodaje ovaj automobil. (He is selling this car at a high price.)
5. *Skupo* smo platili tu grešku. (We paid dearly for that mistake.)
6. Kvalitetna hrana ponekad može biti *skuplja*. (Quality food can sometimes be more expensive.)
7. *Skupi* ukrasi ulepšavaju ovo mesto. (Expensive decorations beautify this place.)
8. Bilo je *skupo* za naučiti tu lekciju. (It was costly to learn that lesson.)
9. Oni žive u *skupoj* četvrti grada. (They live in an expensive part of the city.)
10. *Skupim* koracima je krenuo prema izlazu. (He walked toward the exit with expensive steps.)